News & Announcements

 
Our Youth Day will be held on Sunday, June 12 at 10:30 this year.  We will honor all of our graduates at this service as well.  Our speaker will be Reverend Keon A. Gerow from The Catalyst for Change Church.  You can learn more about Reverend Gerow by clicking on the following link. http://www.achangeiscoming.org/pastortext.htm 
 

 

Congratulations to Da'Rel Scott for being drafted to the New York Giants!!! We are so proud of you, Da'Rel.  You will remain in our prayers as you continue with your success!
 
 
 
St. Paul's would like to extend a special thanks to Myrna Graham for her many years of service to our beloved church. Her presence in the pulpit will surely be missed by all. It is good to know that she is doing better and continues to get stronger. Our prayers and thoughts are with her.
 
Thank you again Pastor Graham and best wishes.
 
St. Paul's Baptist Church, Conshohocken
